@startmindmap
<style>
:depth(0) {
    BackgroundColor #FF5F46
    LineColor #FF5F46
    FontColor #ffffff
    LineThickness 3.0
}
:depth(1) {
    BackgroundColor #0078D4
    LineColor #0078D4
    LineThickness 3.0
    FontColor #FFFFFF
}
:depth(2) {
    BackgroundColor #ffb900
    LineColor #ffb900
    LineThickness 3.0
    FontColor #000000
}
boxless {
    FontColor #000000
}
</style>
+ Choose the\nRight SQL Method
++ CTAS
+++_ Initial load / one-time migration
+++_ Creates new table from query
+++_ Fails if table already exists
++ CREATE OR REPLACE
+++_ Periodic full refreshes
+++_ Replaces entire table
+++_ Preserves permissions
-- COPY INTO
---_ Ongoing file ingestion
---_ Incremental / idempotent loads
---_ Appends to existing table
-- Decision Guide
---_ First time? → CTAS
---_ Full periodic reload? → CREATE OR REPLACE
---_ Regular file arrivals? → COPY INTO
---_ Complex file detection? → Auto Loader
@endmindmap
